									<h2>Stepping Off Shore and into Sea Country</h2>
									<h3>Along the Australian coast, tens of thousands of years’ worth of Indigenous history lies a short dive below the sea’s surface. The hard part is finding it.</h3>
									<p class="insidepagethumbinfodate">Feb 2, 2021 | 2,600 words, about 13 minutes</p>
								</header>
								</a>
							</article>
																				<article class="col insidepagethumbholder rotator ">
								<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/features/sunken-bridge-size-continent/" class="tagmanager" id="Related_article_16193" >
